:"苏格兰阿吉爾","lifeSummary":"当Giolla Adomnan mac Solaim于大约1065年出生在苏格兰阿吉爾易斯萊 易曼德时，他的父亲Solomh MacMeargaigh, King of Dublin27岁，母亲Hvarflad37岁。他于1080年之前与Thora Inen MacFergus在苏格兰结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。他去世于大约1150年在爱尔兰享年87岁，埋葬在爱尔兰。"},"hr":{"Abt 1065–about 1150":"oko 1065.–oko 1150.","1065–1150":"1065–1150.","–1067":"–1067","1060–1080":"1060–1080.","1080–1164":"1080.–1164","1085–1123":"1085–1123","1040–1083":"1040–1083.","1030–1070":"1030–1070","1080":"1080.","about 1150":"oko 1150.","1164":"1164","1065":"1065","1030":"1030","1085":"1085","1150":"1150.","1040":"1040","1083":"1083.","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","Abt 1065":"oko 1065.","1123":"1123","1067":"1067","before 1080":"prije 1080.","24 Apr 1070":"24. travnja 1070.","Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland":"Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland","Hebrides, Scotland":"Hebrides, Škotska, United Kingdom","Ireland":"Irska","Morven, Argyll, Scotland":"Morven, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland"},"cs":{"Abt 1065–about 1150":"okolo 1065–okolo 1150","1065–1150":"1065–1150","–1067":"–1067","1060–1080":"1060–1080","1080–1164":"1080–1164","1085–1123":"1085–1123","1040–1083":"1040–1083","1030–1070":"1030–1070","1080":"1080","about 1150":"okolo 1150","1164":"1164","1065":"1065","1030":"1030","1085":"1085","1150":"1150","1040":"1040","1083":"1083","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","Abt 1065":"okolo 1065","1123":"1123","1067":"1067","before 1080":"před 1080","24 Apr 1070":"24. dubna 1070","Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland":"Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland","Hebrides, Scotland":"Hebrides, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Ireland":"Irsko","Morven, Argyll, Scotland":"Morven, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland"},"da":{"Abt 1065–about 1150":"omkring 1065–omkring 1150","1065–1150":"1065–1150","–1067":"–1067","1060–1080":"1060–1080","1080–1164":"1080–1164","1085–1123":"1085–1123","1040–1083":"1040–1083","1030–1070":"1030–1070","1080":"1080","about 1150":"omkring 1150","1164":"1164","1065":"1065","1030":"1030","1085":"1085","1150":"1150","1040":"1040","1083":"1083","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","Abt 1065":"omkring 1065","1123":"1123","1067":"1067","before 1080":"før 1080","24 Apr 1070":"24. april 1070","Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland":"Islay Island, Argyll, Skotland","Hebrides, Scotland":"Hebrides, Skotland, United Kingdom","Ireland":"Irland","Morven, Argyll, Scotland":"Morven, Argyll, Skotland","Scotland":"Skotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Skotland"},"nl":{"Abt 1065–about 1150":"circa 1065–circa 1150","1065–1150":"1065–1150","–1067":"–1067","1060–1080":"1060–1080","1080–1164":"1080–1164","1085–1123":"1085–1123","1040–1083":"1040–1083","1030–1070":"1030–1070","1080":"1080","about 1150":"circa 1150","1164":"1164","1065":"1065","1030":"1030","1085":"1085","1150":"1150","1040":"1040","1083":"1083","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","Abt 1065":"circa 1065","1123":"1123","1067":"1067","before 1080":"vóór 1080","24 Apr 1070":"24 april 1070","Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland":"Islay Island, Argyll, Schotland","Hebrides, Scotland":"Hebrides, Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk","Ireland":"Ierland","Morven, Argyll, Scotland":"Morven, Argyll, Schotland","Scotland":"Schotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Schotland"},"en":{"Abt 1065–about 1150":"about 1065–about 1150","1065–1150":"1065–1150","–1067":"–1067","1060–1080":"1060–1080","1080–1164":"1080–1164","1085–1123":"1085–1123","1040–1083":"1040–1083","1030–1070":"1030–1070","1080":"1080","about 1150":"about 1150","1164":"1164","1065":"1065","1030":"1030","1085":"1085","1150":"1150","1040":"1040","1083":"1083","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","Abt 1065":"about 1065","1123":"1123","1067":"1067","before 1080":"before 1080","24 Apr 1070":"24 April 1070","Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland":"Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland","Hebrides, Scotland":"Hebrides, Scotland, United Kingdom","Ireland":"Ireland","Morven, Argyll, Scotland":"Morven, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","nameMeanings":[{"name":"mac","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  Vietnamese Cuong, Minh, Lien, Muoi, Thanh, Tho, Tieu, Vinh, Anh, Beo, Binh, Chau.","Chinese: variant Romanization of the surnames 麥 (see   Mai   2) and 莫 (see   Mo   1).","Vietnamese (<b>Mạc</b>): from Chinese 莫 ‘nothing; nonexistent’; see   Mo   1."],"variants":[{"name":"Mai","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  Vietnamese Hung, Thanh, Hoa, Son, Dung, Long, Binh, Minh, Thu, Hue, Huong, Thuy.  Chinese Chi, Hong, Ho, Sang, Han, Hang, Jian, Li, Man, Mei, Sen, Wei.","Chinese: Mandarin form of the surname 麥, meaning ‘wheat’ in Chinese: (i) from Mai Qiu (麥丘), the title of a man in the state of Qi (located mainly in present-day Shandong province) during the Spring and Autumn period (770–476  BC ), who, despite being very old, came to celebrate the birthday of the Duke Huan of Qi (ruler of the state of Qi, died 643  BC ). His descendants inherited 麥, the first part of his title, as their surname. (ii) borne by descendants of Mai Tie Zhang (麥鐵杖), a famous general during the Sui dynasty (581–618  AD ). His descendants were scattered around southern China.","Chinese: Mandarin and Cantonese form of the surname 買, meaning ‘buy’ in Chinese: (i) borne by descendants of the king Song Weizi, founder of the state of Song. (ii) borne by descendants of the Duke Dao of Xu (ruler of the state of Xu, 546–523  BC ), possibly inheriting his personal name. (iii) from the first element of the personal name Mai Zhu Chu (買朱鉏), style name of an official who lived during the Spring and Autumn period (770–476  BC ). (iv) it has also been traced back to other ethnic groups in northern China."]}]},{"name":"Giolla","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  German Dieter, Alois, Erwin, Gunter.  Indian Vinay, Krishna, Padma, Prasad, Satyanarayana.","Germanized or Americanized form of Sorbian <b>Góla</b> and Polish   Gola  .","East German: habitational name from any of the places called Gollau, in Lower Saxony, East Prussia, and Bavaria."],"variants":[{"name":"Gola","meanings":["Of Russian origin, a contracted form of  <b>Galina</b> , which is said to be from the Greek name <i>Galēnē</i> ‘calm’, although it may actually be a vernacular form of   Helen .  The name is now adopted occasionally by English-speakers, perhaps influenced by the festive connotations of the vocabulary word."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Giolla Adomnan mac Solaim was born about 1065, in Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland, his father, Solomh MacMeargaigh, King of Dublin, was 27 and his mother, Hvarflad, was 37. He married Thora Inen MacFergus before 1080, in Scotland. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died about 1150, in Ireland, at the age of 87, and was buried in Ireland."},"et":{"Abt 1065–about 1150":"umbes 1065–umbes 1150","1065–1150":"1065–1150","–1067":"–1067","1060–1080":"1060–1080","1080–1164":"1080–1164","1085–1123":"1085–1123","1040–1083":"1040–1083","1030–1070":"1030–1070","1080":"1080","about 1150":"umbes 1150","1164":"1164","1065":"1065","1030":"1030","1085":"1085","1150":"1150","1040":"1040","1083":"1083","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","Abt 1065":"umbes 1065","1123":"1123","1067":"1067","before 1080":"enne 1080","24 Apr 1070":"24. aprill 1070","Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland":"Islay Island, Argyll, Scotland","Hebrides, Scotland":"Hebrides, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Ireland":"Iirimaa","Morven, Argyll, Scotland":"Morven, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland"},"fi":{"Abt 1065–about 1150":"noin 1065–noin 1150","1065–1150":"1065–1150","–1067":"–1067","1060–1080":"1060–1080","1080–1164":"1080–1164","1085–1123":"1085–1123","1040–1083":"1040–1083","1030–1070":"1030–1070","1080":"1080","about 1150":"noin 1150","1164":"1164","1065":"1065","1030":"1030","1085":"1085","1150":"1150","1040":"1040","1083":"1083","1060":"10